9 An Act relating to professional licensing fees;
amending 59 O.S. 2021, Section 858-625, which relates
10 to fees for the Home Inspection Licensing Act;
increasing certain fees; amending 59 O.S. 2021,
11 Section 1000.5, which relates to the Construction
Industries Board Act; establishing certain fees for
12 license or permit issuance or renewal; amending 59
O.S. 2021, Section 1686.1, which relates to poultry
13 house contractor license; conforming language;
updating statutory references; updating statutory
14 language; and providing an effective date.
15
16
17 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
