9 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 1000.5, is
10 amended to read as follows:
11 Section 1000.5. A. The Construction Industries Board may
12 establish a system of fees by rule to be charged for the application
13 for licenses, for the issuance and renewal of licenses and permits,
14 for administration of examinations, for formal project reviews, and
15 dishonored checks under the Board’s authority. This provision is
16 subject to the following limitations:
17 1. No schedule of fees may be established or amended by the
18 Board except during such times as the Legislature is in session;
19 provided, the Board may establish or amend a schedule of fees at a
20 time when the Legislature is not in session if the fees or schedule
21 of fees has been specifically authorized by the Legislature pursuant
22 to paragraph 2 of this subsection. The Board must follow the
23 procedures required by Article I of the Administrative Procedures
