18 environmentally controlled poultry houses;
19 3. A listing of the names and social security numbers of all
20 employees and laborers working in this state who will be involved in
21 wiring a poultry house for environmentally controlled poultry
22 houses. The social security number information shall remain with
23 the Board as confidential and privileged except for necessary
24 disclosures to state agencies to verify compliance with requirements
