6 F. The Board shall suspend the poultry house contractor license
7 when the licensee fails to:
8 1. Maintain liability insurance coverage;
9 2. Maintain satisfactory workers’ compensation coverage under
10 the Administrative Workers’ Compensation Act or provide an affidavit
